Package: VisualMWM
Type: Package
Title: R functions to visualize Morris water maze data
Version: 0.0.0.9003
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "David",
           family = "Thonnard",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "thonnard.david@gmail.com")
Maintainer: David Thonnard <thonnard.david@gmail.com>
Description: This R package provides functions to visualize Morris water maze tracking data in motion! 
    The goal is to visualize behaviour starting from raw, unprocessed data, i.e. x and y coordinates for every time point, 
    that is obtained with tracking software (e.g. Ethovision). 
Depends: 
    R (>= 4.2.0),
    ggplot2 (>= 3.3.6)
License: GPL-3 | file LICENSE
BugReports: https://github.com/Thonnard/VisualMWM/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
